driving directions to lakeland brewery
From Orland to Lakeland
Take I-4 to exit 25 for County Line Road. Take a right on N County Line Road and then your first left on to Southside Frontage Road. Brew Hub is located approximately 2 miles down on the right.
From Tampa to Lakeland
Take I-4 to exit 25 for County Line Road. Take a right on N County Line Road and then your first left on to Southside Frontage Road. Brew Hub is located approximately 2 miles down on the right.
From Lakeland, FL
Travel west on Polk Parkway/FL-570. Take exit 1 for Clark Road and continue straight through two stoplights. Take a right on Southside Frontage Road and Brew Hub is located approximately 1 mile down on the right.
